40:42.291 --> 40:44.691
I don't know.

40:45.544 --> 40:48.012
Sometimes I think...

40:48.037 --> 40:51.004
proof's all around us.

40:53.120 --> 40:56.021
You're almost there.
You're doing great.

40:56.046 --> 40:57.548
- Whoa, whoa, whoa.
