40:57.573 --> 40:58.605
I got him. I got him right here.

40:58.607 --> 40:59.739
Hold him. Oh. You good?

40:59.741 --> 41:01.775
Here we go.

41:01.777 --> 41:03.176
- Be more careful.
- Yeah.

41:03.201 --> 41:05.668
Be careful.

